name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: GitHub Add color to recently not updated file

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add color to recently not updated file on GitHub.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
GitHub Add color to recently not updated file.

The file which is not updated more than half a year is changed into 'orange'. 
The file which is not updated more than one year is changed into 'red'.
